title: Star Wars: The Force Unleashed (PS2) (PAL) (Fabio5ilva)
description:
Star Wars: The Force Unleashed (PS2)

Region: PAL

Year: 2008

This entry in the Star Wars saga casts players as Darth Vader's "Secret Apprentice", unveiling new revelations about the Star Wars galaxy. The expansive story, created under direction from George Lucas, is set during the largely unexplored era between Star Wars: Episode III Revenge of the Sith and Star Wars: Episode IV A New Hope. Featuring unique gameplay features designed for the PlayStation 2, Star Wars: The Force Unleashed has players as this new mercenary villain assisting Vader in his quest to rid the universe of Jedi - and facing decisions that could change the course of their destiny.
